%% AI action approval lifecycle. See 07-approval-domain.md
stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> draft
  draft --> pending
  draft --> cancelled
  pending --> approved: human decidedBy (never restricted)
  pending --> rejected: human decidedBy
  pending --> expired
  pending --> cancelled
  approved --> executing: ONLY path to execution
  approved --> cancelled
  executing --> completed
  executing --> failed: carries rollbackMetadata
  rejected --> [*]
  expired --> [*]
  completed --> [*]
  failed --> [*]
  cancelled --> [*]
